To create a new module, run `cd /home/sandy/source_repos/odoo && uv run ./odoo-bin app_name project_base_directory`
Then edit manifest to have proper 
name
summary
description
author will be Uniquity Ventures
website will be https://uniquity.in
Don't leave these as the default values
If it depends on other modules, add that in the depends list
Add in the paths of all the files in data list
For a bridge module, the name is b_app1_name_app2_name